snippet: A student at the University of Maryland shot his two roommates, one fatally, near the College Park campus before killing himself, the authorities said.
abstract: University of Maryland graduate student Dayvon Green shoots his two roommates, before killing himself; one roommate, Stephen Alex Rane, dies of his wounds, while second remains in stable condition.
lead_paragraph: A student at the University of Maryland shot his two roommates, one fatally, near the College Park campus before killing himself, the authorities said.
